title: Auto Gordian Knot 2.45 (Auto GK)
description: The tool for ripping DVD's to Xvid and/or Divx. This software is used by the greatest ripper ever, AXXO. It can rip your movies to the famous good quality of Axxo's rips: 700 MB, MP3 audio, XVID very good quality. You don't have to install any other programs, AutoGK will do it for you. This is the latest stable version of the tool (don't mess with beta stuff, could be dangerous). It has a tutorial, but whenever you have a question and don't want to look in the tutorial, please post a comment, and seed!
